[SN]TITLE[SN]
Football Leaks quiz: Mario Balotelli bonuses, Zlatan Ibrahimovic goals, Paul Pogba cash

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A book published in Germany this week claims to reveal some of the astronomical sums being spent in world football.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Football Leaks: The Dirty Business of Football discloses some eye-popping sums apparently involved in football's biggest transfers, from Manchester United's world-record signing of Paul Pogba to Ezequiel Lavezzi's lucrative move from Paris St-Germain to the Chinese Super League.
We have delved into the book and put together this quiz from its alleged sums, so get playing.
